Stars: Lon Chaney Jr., John Carradine
Directors: Harold Daniels, Reginald Le Borg, Jerry Warren

In this Belly Dance of Horror, Chaney and Carradine play warlock brothers who use their powers and covens of witches to battle over the family fortune.
